Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:23.25,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,V noci 28. januára
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:29.00,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvôli dažďu, bolo chladno.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:33.66,RAINBOW Whisper,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to Ishihara, An-chan! Začal konať!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:34.75,RAINBOW Whisper,,0000,0000,0000,,Počuješ ma, An-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:36.03,RAINBOW Whisper,,0000,0000,0000,,Počuješ ma, An-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:38.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeho cieľom je určite ten list!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:41.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Určite vie aj o našom úkryte!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:42.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pohni sa! Musíš to povedať Setsuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:43.66,RAINBOW Whisper,,0000,0000,0000,,Pohni sa! Musíš to povedať Setsuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:48.75,RAINBOW Whisper,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs52}An-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.63,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Setsuko-san si nerob starosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:51.53,RAINBOW Whisper,,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:53.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:55.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... že cieľom Ishihary...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:57.95,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... som iba ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počúvaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Budeš v bezpečí tam, kde si.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ostatné nechaj na mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:09.57,RAINBOW Whisper,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:10.79,RAINBOW Whisper,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs52}An-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:17.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pán prekladateľ. Prosím oznámte moju vďačnosť tomuto dôstojníkovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:18.42,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:20.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:24.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ešte...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem, aby išiel za Mariom, a povedal mu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:31.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť, že nemôžem vidieť\N tvoj boj.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:36.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pane...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:40.57,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urobili ste dobre, že ste ho nechal ísť?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:47.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoríš, že som ho nemal nechať ísť?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oči toho japonského chlapa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:55.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pred 11 rokmi som sa pri pohľade na ne triasol.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:00.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ničoho sa nebojí... je zmierený...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:01.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To sú oči...{\alphaFF} {\i1}kamikadze{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To sú oči... {\i1}kamikadze{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buď ako muž, a drž sa vonku čo najdlhšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:25.94,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:32.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier! Gratulujeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:35.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neopováž sa sem vrátiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:38.78,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj na nás! Pod stromom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Predstavíš mi svoje dievča, keď odtiaľto odídem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.26,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráťte sa do cely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lebo pôjdete na samotku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.63,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoji priatelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:51.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:56.76,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni sú moji najdôležitejší priatelia s\N ktorými som sa tu stretol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:20.42,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}"Keby som odišiel sám,\N nikomu by sa nič nestalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.05,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Je to osud?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:28.60,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Pokiaľ sa nepostarám o toho prekliateho chlapa, \Nmoji priatelia nikdy nebudú mať šťastie..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:33.52,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Sakuragi Rokurouta bol na to pripravený.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:39.21,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to, že sa ti dobre darí, \NSakuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. A ako tebe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:45.03,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko po starom. Len...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:49.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka tebe, ešte stále dýcham.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo z toho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si odporný.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:06.89,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie si o nič lepší ako besný\N túlavý pes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:10.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si len kus hovna čo porušuje zákon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezdá sa ti to divné, Sakuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je to divné?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo taký zasraný hajzel ako ty, \Nmôže byť šťastný?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedáva to žiaden zmysel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:29.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Najprv utečieš, a potom si žiješ na vidieku,\N ako keby sa nič nestalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:34.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo? Prečo musím žiť so všetkým stresom \Na strachom iba ja?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:40.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To už stačí! Tu sa to všetko ukončí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:46.79,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme to ukončiť, Sakuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je s tebou, chlape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:56.77,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš poraziť Američana, s pravačkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:06:01.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počúvaj. Nesnaž sa ho zraziť dole jednou ranou.\N Používaj aj ľavú ruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak to chcem aj urobiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:04.35,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak to chcem urobiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.17,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sekundanti z ringu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lilly-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V ďalšom kole vám ukážem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.61,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... porážku Ameriky...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.22,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukážem vám to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:37.22,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš si, že ma dokážeš zabiť \Niba pomocou pištole?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Budem prvý kto ťa zabije!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:48.67,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom to dievča! Tu suku, \Nzdravotnú sestru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.22,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je príliš dobrá pre teba! Budem ju znásilňovať \Nznova a znova!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:55.01,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom si podám tvojich kamošov. \NVšetkých!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:58.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabijem ich bolestivo a pomaly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:01.69,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Budem mať, toľko zábavy Sakuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:35.35,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zopakuj to ešte raz, Ishihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:41.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo budeš robiť s mojimi priateľmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:05.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemá žiadnu šancu na víťazstvo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zatiaľ nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:10.91,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále je to tam...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odvaha v jeho očiach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.52,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Len blafuješ, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:38.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne?! Nemáš gule!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáš gule, na...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.63,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezabíjaj mňa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To bol posledný náboj.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:09.42,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz ma už nezabiješ, Ishihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.23,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezahrávaj sa so mnou. \N Nedovolím aby to takto skončilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:24.61,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedá sa to už vrátiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:27.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zomrieš buď ty, alebo ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.57,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.12,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže toto si hľadal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:58.61,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukončíme to už...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:15.38,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario! {\alphaFF}Máš len jedinú šancu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.97,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario! Máš len jedinú šancu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.82,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,V momente, keď nebude dávať pozor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:23.80,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,... zaútoč na jeho pravá stranu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:25.91,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,V tom momente!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.90,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Sledujte pozorne, Lilly-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.75,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Amerika...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.13,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,... prehraje!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:51.79,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)} Americký vojak padol do pasce\N pripravenej Máriom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:11:00.23,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}V tom istom čase, ale na inom mieste začalo \Nposledné kolo medzi Sakuragim a Ishiharom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:05.90,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Obaja boli ochotní obetovať všetko čo ešte mali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.06,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč. {\alphaFF}Hagino.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.91,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč. Hagino.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:15.01,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím o pochopenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:19.14,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,To, čo urobili Ishihara a Sasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.83,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Čím všetkým si si musel v živote prejsť...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.41,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko, čo si mal v srdci...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.22,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,List na rozlúčku, ktorý obsahoval všetko, čo sa dialo ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:32.33,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa chystám dať Ishiharovi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.80,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.31,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj sa ospravedlňujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:41.18,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Sakuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.63,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si to urobil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:55.17,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem to už ukončiť. To je všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:58.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keby to tak nebolo, Ishihara...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:01.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nič by sa ti nestalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nerob zo mňa hlupáka-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:13.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.95,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neprosím ťa o láskavosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:21.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nedovolím, aby si sa priblížil \Nk mojím priateľom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:23.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.03,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už... {\alphaFF}nemáme nič spoločného.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:33.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už ... Nemáme nič spoločného.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.90,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš urobiť s tým listom,\N čo len chceš,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ale ak... {\alphaFF}máš nejaké svedomie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ale ak... máš nejaké svedomie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:46.67,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... polož kvety na jeho hrob.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:02.93,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"Šťastie Setsuko a ostatných šiestich záleží od tohto listu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.21,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.00,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,pochop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.10,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,A odpusť mi..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:13.05,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Sakuragi sa rozhodol ospravedlniť Haginovy neskôr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\fs60\pos(640,70)}Dva!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\fs60\pos(640,70)}Tri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:27.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten chlapec je dobrý! \NNaozaj porazil Američana!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, pozri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.52,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\fs60\pos(640,70)}Štyri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:30.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\fs60\pos(640,70)}Päť!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.51,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moment. Ako že ešte môže vstať?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\fs60\pos(640,70)}Šesť!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:42.43,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Americky vojak. Nie je niekto, kto ľahko prehraje\N kvôli jednej rane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\fs60\pos(640,70)}Sedem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:41.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\fs60\pos(640,70)}Osem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, chlapče! Ukáž mi, čo dokážeš!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokonči to svojou pravačkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.00,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Bude to naozaj tak jednoduché?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.29,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,S mojou zničenou rukou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.57,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}"Prosím, nevstávaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.97,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Prosím, lež na zemi"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:07.67,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Bohužiaľ pre Maria, Americký vojak\N sa v ringu postavil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:10.13,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}... a zaujal boxerskú pózu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:14.78,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}"Môj súper je muž! \NOn je boxer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:19.41,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Boj medzi mužmi znovu začal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.11,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo mám urobiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Sakuragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:57.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi... Ako také hnusné psisko, ako ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... môže viesť takýto život?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\t(0,3100,\fscx150\fscy150)\fad(0,800)}SAKURAGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:32.66,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím...  Počkaj, Sakuragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.72,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, počúvaj čo ti chcem povedať...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.20,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Američania...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú tvrdí...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:53.88,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, ako An-chan povedal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Udrel som ho svojou ľavačkou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.51,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale vieš...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.34,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... ten Američan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.90,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... ten Američan... aj tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.58,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... dokázal vstať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to šialené...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To už stačí chlapče!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.61,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dal si zo seba už všetko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:15.34,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto ti to nebude mať za zlé, ak vycúvaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:18.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rád by som...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.69,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak poviem rozhodcovi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:21.76,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo by urobil An-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.35,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo by si urobil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bojoval by si ďalej, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.30,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chlapče...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.91,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sekundanti z ringu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.63,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.36,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevzdám sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:50.64,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:59.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemám ti už čo povedať.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy nás už nehľadaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:07.07,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už nikdy sa nám neukazuj na oči!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:10.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Len som chcel zarobiť\N nejaké peniaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:15.25,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki na mňa tlačil, nemohol som odmietnuť!\N Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:18.12,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy by ma nenapadlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}... že spácha samovraždu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.77,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bál som sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:30.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále som sa bál, že...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebudem už strážnikom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:42.23,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo mám teraz urobiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.26,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo mám teraz urobiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:49.35,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz mi, Sakuragi! \NPovedz mi to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:54.52,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz mi to, Sakuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.66,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty to vieš, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.60,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Však, Sakuragi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:02.18,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:11.26,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Čepeľ v jeho tele sa zdala byť chladná,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.17,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,ale po chvíli začala horieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.28,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolí, Sakuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.16,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolí to, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty sviňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:33.39,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne si zvrátený...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:42.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš ma takto zabiť, {\alphaFF}Ishihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.22,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš ma takto zabiť, Ishihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.12,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odíď, Ishihara...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:52.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:54.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odíď...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.91,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal som ti, zmizni... ISHIHARA!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-On nemôže umrieť ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bez ohľadu na to, čo robím, on neumiera ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:26.59,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bez ohľadu na to, ako sa snažím,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:30.00,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nikdy nezničím jeho dušu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.51,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:50.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to robíš chlapče?! \NUdieraj viac z prava!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôže to urobiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:58.20,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Od samého začiatku bojujem so zranenou rukou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:04.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To už stačí! Jednoducho sa len \Nrýchlo vzdaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.49,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľúbil som...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:12.19,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Musíš vyhrať, Mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.92,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chanovi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.03,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Som sľúbil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.65,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan mi povedal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:30.35,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,... aby som vyhral!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:34.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200}Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:37.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Polícia! Vzdajte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odhoď ten nôž!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.39,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:49.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, o tom niet pochýb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.69,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je... {\alphaFF}Sakuragi Rokurouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je... Sakuragi Rokurouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:00.20,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Sily ho opúšťala po veľkej strate krvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:05.66,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Slabými, trasúcimi krokmi, sa Sakuragi vybral k ringu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:11.18,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}"Chcem to vidieť. Okamih, keď sa Mario stáva mužom ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.87,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Sakuragi myslel len na to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.92,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Spolu s dažďovými kvapkami, padli aj výstrely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:36.89,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Padajúci Sakuragi vidí tváre priateľov!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:38.24,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}A potom...
